title: ALL NEW: Pro Photo West Magazine Summer 2014 ~ Lindsay Adler
description:
It's here, our all new Pro Photo West Summer 2014 issue. Expanding on our new design and layout, we continue to shake up the industry, and redefine the ultimate Professional Photographers magazine. For the first time, our readers get access to exclusive discounts on photo gear, thanks to our agreement with Greentoe.com. Greentoe.com is changing how photographers can buy lenses, cameras, and other equipment with discounts as high as 30% off most retail prices. To access this PPC benefit, simply visit the digital version of our magazine and click on any of the highlighted product links. That will open the Greentoe.com website, and you will automatically qualify for the best savings. Read our interview with the founder of Greentoe.com, Joe Marapodi, to learn more.

In the Summer issue you'll also discover:

- An exclusive interview with Lindsay Adler
- A first look at the PENTAX 645Z
- A full review of the revolutionary Profoto B1
- A 2014 State Photographic IMAGE COMPETITION special
- Tutorials
- and so much more.

Pro Photo West is the #1 award winning PPA affiliate publication in the USA, and exclusively created by the Professional Photographers of California. Published quarterly, we feature exceptional artists from all over the world, product reviews, tutorials, education, and information to beginning and experienced photographers alike.
